data.description: ***$5000 CLOSING COST CREDIT WITH REASONABLE OFFER***Welcome to 26 Stonewood – where elegance meets functionality on a sprawling 1-acre oasis. This gorgeous 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts over 2500 square feet of living space, exquisite stone countertops, painted kitchen cabinets, and luxury white built in shutters just to name a few! The heart of this property is the expansive fenced yard, providing both security and serenity for your loved ones and pets.  Outdoor enthusiasts will adore the firepit, perfect for gathering under the New Mexico stars. The spacious driveway ensures ample parking for guests or recreational vehicles, while the workshop is a handyman's dream, ready to bring your creative projects to life.  Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or an entertainer's paradise, this property offers the best of both worlds. Located just outside of Alamogordo, you'll enjoy the convenience of city amenities while savoring rural living. Schedule a showing today!
